[0.3, "o", "  \u001b[0;36m\u2551\u001b[0m\u001b[1m   Demo 5: \"Dashboard \u2014 Fleet Control\"                      \u001b[0;36m\u2551\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.3, "o", "  \u001b[0;36m\u2551\u001b[0m\u001b[2m   Platform: YouTube / LinkedIn \u2014 web UI showcase Length: ~90s Audience: Team leads, security engineers Setup: Multiple pods already running (e.g. claude-code, openclaw, browser)\u001b[0;36m\u2551\u001b[0m\r\n"]
